name: HEN-QUALITY
description: HEN-QUALITY is my first piece on HEN and i truly couldn’t think of a piece that represents my position in this world. I'm a very unsaturated, basic, typical human. However I have been fortunate enough to have a handful of friends who pushed the agenda for what the “norm” is. They have faced hardships I may never endure and in the face of adversity they stand up for what they believe in. I support anyone, especially those with a voice as one day I might be in a position where I need people to HEAR me. Not COMMNAD OR DEMEAN. We are equals and that is what I love the most about the NFT Space so far. Enjoy!
